These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, chinese, thai, nigerian, australian, british
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, epic, comedy, disaster, documentary, satire
 1. the person watching superhero movies is the indonesian##1
 2. the australian is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the australian is somewhere to the left of the thai##5
 4. the chinese is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5
 5. the person watching superhero movies is the indonesian##1
 6. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 7. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the thai is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 9. the pakistani is on the left of the chinese##1
10. the nigerian is the person watching documentary movies##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
12. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
13. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
14. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching epic movies##5
15. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the nigerian##5
16. the thai is the person watching scientific movies##1
17. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
18. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the australian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |     6     |      7      |
| Nationality    | british    | nigerian  | australian       | indonesian | pakistani | chinese | thai        |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | documentary | epic | superhero    | satire   | comedy   | scientific |

