.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bolivar, havana, tiparillo, cain, davidoff, pall-mall
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, scooter, bus, snowmobile, subway, taxi
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 2. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 3. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the right of the chaman-smoker##5
 6. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
 7. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
10. the person driving the subway is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
12. the havana-smoker is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
13. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3
14. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
15. the havana-smoker is the person driving the quad-bike##1
16. the person driving the quad-bike is the havana-smoker##1
17. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3    |    4    |       5       |     6     |    7     |
| Cigar   | bolivar    | chaman | davidoff     | cain | havana | pall-mall     | tiparillo |
