.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-5-3::.
There 7 different types of food: cucumber, watermelon, apricot, zucchini, asparagus, pomegranate, lime
City: hannover, prague, liverpool, berlin, hamburg, boston, miami
 1. the person traveling to prague is the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person eating pomegranate is in an even position##4
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to liverpool and the person eating lime##2
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the left of the person eating asparagus##5
 6. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
 7. the person eating asparagus is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
10. the person traveling to liverpool is the person traveling to liverpool##1
11. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
12. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
13. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person eating apricot##5
14. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
15. the person eating zucchini is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |       3       |     4     |      5       |      6      |    7    |
