 3. the person who's hobby is iced-tea-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##5
