 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
11. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is iced-tea-climbing##3
12. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
