14. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
15. the person driving the car is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
16. the person watching comedy movies is in an even position##4
17. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person driving the car##1
18. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |       5       |      6       |   7    |
| Transport     | snowmobile   | car | roller | taxi | bike         | helicopter | bus  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | scientific   | disaster  | documentary   | western | comedy   | romance |

